                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant E</hi> 4.) On Friday the 4th of December, I went and took Miller in charge—he said he bought the pigs of Wiggins and Carter for 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. Mr. Andrews identified them.</p>
